54
00:03:47,608 --> 00:03:48,241
Okay?

55
00:03:49,443 --> 00:03:50,109
I'll wait for you

56
00:03:52,179 --> 00:03:52,845
Does it still hurt?

57
00:04:04,758 --> 00:04:05,324
Your Highness

58
