He certainly wouldn't let someone he loves

65
00:04:19,773 --> 00:04:20,907
Fall into danger

66
00:04:21,108 --> 00:04:23,242
But that spirit remaining in
the Northest Land is a disaster

67
00:04:24,445 --> 00:04:25,044
Your Highness

68
00:04:26,013 --> 00:04:27,246
What do you plan to do?

69
00:04:40,260 --> 00:04:41,427
To capture

70
