Look what she's done to you

74
00:05:12,459 --> 00:05:13,159
Bai

75
00:05:13,694 --> 00:05:15,094
You've been with me day and night

76
00:05:15,529 --> 00:05:17,330
It's natural that you
discovered little Isatis's identity

77
