The point is

82
00:05:24,471 --> 00:05:25,838
She's not even human

83
00:05:26,273 --> 00:05:27,473
Us ordinary folks can't

84
00:05:27,474 --> 00:05:29,041
Fight against the Supreme Clarity Division

85
00:05:29,843 --> 00:05:30,776
If you ask me

86
00:05:30,777 --> 00:05:31,978
Before anything bad happens

87
00:05:31,979 --> 00:05:34,313
We should send this lady away quickly

88
00:05:37,050 --> 00:05:37,617
What's 'this?

89
00:05:41,355 --> 00:05:43,122
Why did you draw a piece of grass on your arm?

90
00:05:43,357 --> 00:05:44,490
