91
00:05:45,526 --> 00:05:46,926
She and I have formed a spirit bond

92
00:05:47,194 --> 00:05:48,194
Together in life and in harm

93
00:05:49,196 --> 00:05:50,229
This is the proof

94
00:05:50,998 --> 00:05:51,430
Together?

95
00:05:51,798 --> 00:05:52,798
Spirit bond?

96
00:05:54,668 --> 00:05:56,235
She must have cast a spell on you

97
